text.section:
This section applies to any sheriff or deputy sheriff engaged in any activity other than those activities relating to:
courthouse security;
service of process;
the transportation of inmates to and from court proceedings;
personnel and other administrative activities;
activities, including activities relating to performing law enforcement functions, arising under a multijurisdictional agreement under the supervision and direction of the Maryland State Police or other State agency; or
any other activities, except activities relating to performing law enforcement functions or detention center functions.
